00:01:23.450 --> 00:01:24.980 align:middle line:84%
How do you do that
with chemtrails?

00:01:24.980 --> 00:01:27.410 align:middle line:10%
>>STEVENS: I wondered
about us then, too.

00:01:27.410 --> 00:01:28.970 align:middle line:10%
I was really good.

00:01:28.970 --> 00:01:31.520 align:middle line:10%
And when you have storm
after storm after storm

00:01:31.520 --> 00:01:35.150 align:middle line:10%
