cliff or a cooling cliff

00:17:24.855 --> 00:17:27.490 align:middle line:90%
that they're trying to delay.

00:17:27.490 --> 00:17:32.020 align:middle line:84%
Otherwise, why spend the ungodly
sums of money that they have,

00:17:32.020 --> 00:17:33.220 align:middle line:90%
to do this?

00:17:33.220 --> 00:17:36.560 align:middle line:84%
And cloak it in such
intense secrecy?

00:17:36.560 --> 00:17:39.160 align:middle line:84%
There's something
that they're hiding.

00:17:39.160 --> 00:17:40.480 align:middle line:90%
And it's big.

00:17:40.480 --> 00:17:43.210 align:middle line:90%
It's really, really big.

00:17:43.210 --> 00:17:46.030 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: If you were to venture
to guess which-- that's what it

00:17:46.030 --> 00:17:48.070 align:middle line:90%
would be, what would you think?

00:17:48.070 --> 00:17:51.175 align:middle line:84%
Aside from the sheer potential
