>>STEVENS: Yes.

00:21:19.345 --> 00:21:19.630 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: More or less.

00:21:19.630 --> 00:21:20.077 align:middle line:84%
>>STEVENS: We will
live through it.

00:21:20.077 --> 00:21:21.827 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Everything
will live through it.

00:21:21.827 --> 00:21:24.200 align:middle line:84%
>>STEVENS: I don't say
we, as in all of us.

00:21:24.200 --> 00:21:27.100 align:middle line:84%
But the majority have
the potential to,

00:21:27.100 --> 00:21:29.185 align:middle line:90%
depending on their preparedness.

00:21:29.185 --> 00:21:31.180 align:middle line:84%
And their ability
and willingness

00:21:31.180 --> 00:21:35.562 align:middle line:84%
to accept difficult times, and
have a positive outlook on it.

00:21:35.562 --> 00:21:37.270 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Yeah, that's
what I was seeing.

00:21:37.270 --> 00:21:38.740 align:middle line:84%
The same thing, that
this is totally-- we

00:21:38.740 --> 00:21:39.614 align:middle line:90%
can get through this.

00:21:39.614 --> 00:21:42.910 align:middle line:84%
>>STEVENS: And at the same
time, this planet barely

00:21:42.910 --> 00:21:45.404 align:middle line:84%
can support the population
