00:21:45.404 --> 00:21:47.695 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Well, certainly
the way we're doing business.

00:21:47.695 --> 00:21:48.310 align:middle line:90%
>>STEVENS: Thank you.

00:21:48.310 --> 00:21:49.225 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Which is
very inefficient.

00:21:49.225 --> 00:21:49.960 align:middle line:84%
>>STEVENS: That's
the difference.

00:21:49.960 --> 00:21:51.370 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: It's not
about the numbers,

00:21:51.370 --> 00:21:53.430 align:middle line:84%
it's about the quality and
the way we're doing business.

00:21:53.430 --> 00:21:54.783 align:middle line:84%
>>STEVENS: And why
