and R-13 insulation

00:23:05.050 --> 00:23:06.520 align:middle line:90%
that's gappy at best.

00:23:06.520 --> 00:23:07.930 align:middle line:90%
It's stupid.

00:23:07.930 --> 00:23:08.846 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: That's true.

00:23:08.846 --> 00:23:09.760 align:middle line:90%
I live in the desert.

