00:23:10.180 --> 00:23:11.050 align:middle line:90%
>>STEVENS: It's not small.

00:23:11.050 --> 00:23:12.175 align:middle line:90%
We should be in the ground.

00:23:12.175 --> 00:23:14.350 align:middle line:84%
Plain and simple, we
should be in the ground.

00:23:14.350 --> 00:23:15.759 align:middle line:90%
It's a great insulator.

00:23:15.759 --> 00:23:17.800 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And there are
experimental communities,

00:23:17.800 --> 00:23:20.770 align:middle line:84%
