have dug into the ground.

00:23:20.770 --> 00:23:21.984 align:middle line:90%
And you have your insulation.

00:23:21.984 --> 00:23:23.650 align:middle line:84%
A little more primitive
housing, though,

00:23:23.650 --> 00:23:25.740 align:middle line:84%
than most people moving
from LA to Phoenix wanted.

00:23:25.740 --> 00:23:26.580 align:middle line:84%
>>STEVENS: Different
from what it used to be.

