It's just not what
we're accustomed to.

00:23:30.550 --> 00:23:30.610 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Exactly.

00:23:30.610 --> 00:23:31.693 align:middle line:90%
It can be quite beautiful.

00:23:31.693 --> 00:23:32.690 align:middle line:90%
>>STEVENS: It can be.

00:23:32.690 --> 00:23:35.140 align:middle line:90%
And very secure, very quiet.

00:23:35.140 --> 00:23:36.940 align:middle line:90%
I don't hear the neighbor's dog.

00:23:36.940 --> 00:23:38.530 align:middle line:84%
I don't hear the
train next door.

00:23:38.530 --> 00:23:38.950 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Well,
not only that, you

