get this incredibly pure
energy of the emanation

00:23:41.440 --> 00:23:44.200 align:middle line:84%
of the Earth itself, rather
than all of this other stuff

00:23:44.200 --> 00:23:46.705 align:middle line:84%
that's bombarding our
entire environment.

00:23:46.705 --> 00:23:47.830 align:middle line:90%
>>STEVENS: It's just noise.

