It's EM noise.

00:23:48.640 --> 00:23:49.713 align:middle line:90%
It's just noise.

00:23:49.713 --> 00:23:50.838 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: But we digressed.

00:23:50.838 --> 00:23:52.815 align:middle line:90%
Enron and weather.

00:23:52.815 --> 00:23:54.190 align:middle line:84%
>>STEVENS: So
Enron, because they

00:23:54.190 --> 00:23:57.340 align:middle line:84%
had this centralized system,
could withhold power.

00:23:57.340 --> 00:23:59.200 align:middle line:84%
They could charge
the local utilities

00:23:59.200 --> 00:24:02.350 align:middle line:84%
a higher rate than-- far higher
