scheme, essentially.

00:24:14.920 --> 00:24:17.609 align:middle line:90%
And they were using debt.

00:24:17.609 --> 00:24:19.400 align:middle line:84%
I don't even know how
to get into all this.

00:24:19.400 --> 00:24:20.290 align:middle line:90%
It's rather complex.

00:24:20.290 --> 00:24:24.230 align:middle line:84%
But Enron being that
centralized power distributor,

00:24:24.230 --> 00:24:30.095 align:middle line:84%
