you lease those power lines.

00:24:35.920 --> 00:24:37.762 align:middle line:90%
You buy that resource.

00:24:37.762 --> 00:24:39.970 align:middle line:84%
And then you resell it when
the heat wave is imminent

00:24:39.970 --> 00:24:42.400 align:middle line:84%
or upon us, and people
are in panic mode,

00:24:42.400 --> 00:24:43.370 align:middle line:90%
at a much higher rate.

