00:44:23.650 --> 00:44:25.810 align:middle line:90%
They can see the wisdom of it.

00:44:25.810 --> 00:44:28.280 align:middle line:84%
They can see that if
the blockchain, meaning

00:44:28.280 --> 00:44:33.130 align:middle line:84%
an immutable, undisputed
record of transactions, then

00:44:33.130 --> 00:44:35.380 align:middle line:84%
the Pentagon wouldn't
have gone up in the press

00:44:35.380 --> 00:44:37.390 align:middle line:84%
conference the day
before 9/11 and say, hey,

00:44:37.390 --> 00:44:39.347 align:middle line:90%
we lost $2.4 trillion dollars.

00:44:39.347 --> 00:44:40.430 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Where did it go?

