>>STEVENS: Where did it go?

00:44:40.870 --> 00:44:41.900 align:middle line:84%
It would all be
on the blockchain.

00:44:41.900 --> 00:44:42.790 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: So there's
a certain amount

00:44:42.790 --> 00:44:44.162 align:middle line:90%
of transparency involved.

00:44:44.162 --> 00:44:45.870 align:middle line:84%
>>STEVENS: That's
exactly what it brings.

00:44:45.870 --> 00:44:47.170 align:middle line:90%
It brings transparency.

