and its value goes up.

00:45:15.280 --> 00:45:18.910 align:middle line:84%
And so, now you can have-- you
would set up a bank account,

00:45:18.910 --> 00:45:22.240 align:middle line:84%
buy your Bitcoin, and then
you can travel with a QR code.

00:45:22.240 --> 00:45:23.840 align:middle line:90%
Most of us know what those are.

00:45:23.840 --> 00:45:27.040 align:middle line:84%
Little block with black digits
in there, and then a code.

00:45:27.040 --> 00:45:30.010 align:middle line:84%
You can go to England
and withdraw it in pound.

00:45:30.010 --> 00:45:32.530 align:middle line:84%
You can go to France
and withdraw it in euro.

00:45:32.530 --> 00:45:35.220 align:middle line:84%
You go to Japan,
withdraw it in yen.

00:45:35.220 --> 00:45:39.530 align:middle line:84%
And so you have this currency
