that stocks are
manipulated up in price,

00:45:54.700 --> 00:45:58.390 align:middle line:84%
there will be a torrent of
funds looking for a safe haven.

00:45:58.390 --> 00:46:01.090 align:middle line:84%
Someplace that can't
be confiscated.

