conservatism versus liberal

00:55:52.300 --> 00:55:53.740 align:middle line:90%
versus progressive.

00:55:53.740 --> 00:56:00.430 align:middle line:84%
That there is a process
of humbling or humiliation

00:56:00.430 --> 00:56:04.690 align:middle line:84%
that we need to go through
as a species in order for any

00:56:04.690 --> 00:56:06.370 align:middle line:90%
of this to really be embraced.

00:56:06.370 --> 00:56:08.490 align:middle line:90%
Can you talk about that?

00:56:08.490 --> 00:56:10.870 align:middle line:84%
>>STEVENS: We kind of
briefly mentioned it earlier,

00:56:10.870 --> 00:56:15.820 align:middle line:84%
that nothing really changes
until you're forced to change.

00:56:15.820 --> 00:56:18.980 align:middle line:84%
I remember a time when my
parents were humbled simply

00:56:18.980 --> 00:56:21.400 align:middle line:84%
because of Dad was
going to school.

00:56:21.400 --> 00:56:25.310 align:middle line:84%
And on my plate, I was probably
six years old at the time,

00:56:25.310 --> 00:56:27.284 align:middle line:90%
