00:56:27.284 --> 00:56:29.660 align:middle line:84%
And I'm like, is
that all we get?

00:56:29.660 --> 00:56:32.150 align:middle line:90%
Is that all we get?

00:56:32.150 --> 00:56:35.870 align:middle line:84%
So we all get to this
point where what we have,

00:56:35.870 --> 00:56:38.220 align:middle line:84%
what we've been comfortable
with, is taken away from us.

00:56:38.220 --> 00:56:41.120 align:middle line:84%
Either we lose a job,
we get into an accident,

00:56:41.120 --> 00:56:43.020 align:middle line:90%
we have a health crisis.

00:56:43.020 --> 00:56:46.520 align:middle line:84%
But as you know, karma
exists at all levels,

00:56:46.520 --> 00:56:50.750 align:middle line:84%
whether it's us as individuals,
family units, genetic history

00:56:50.750 --> 00:56:53.350 align:middle line:90%
lines, or countries.

00:56:53.350 --> 00:56:55.310 align:middle line:90%
And there are karma.

00:56:55.310 --> 00:56:57.830 align:middle line:84%
There's a karma coming back
to this country for the things

00:56:57.830 --> 00:56:59.000 align:middle line:90%
that have happened.

00:56:59.000 --> 00:57:00.710 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And I would
say all countries.

00:57:00.710 --> 00:57:01.280 align:middle line:90%
>>STEVENS: All of them.

00:57:01.280 --> 00:57:02.500 align:middle line:90%
Every unit has a group.

00:57:02.500 --> 00:57:04.430 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: It's a time
of a kind of reckoning

00:57:04.430 --> 00:57:07.040 align:middle line:84%
of our ethical and
moral behaviors.

00:57:07.040 --> 00:57:09.120 align:middle line:84%
>>STEVENS: To bring
us back to center.

00:57:09.120 --> 00:57:10.910 align:middle line:84%
It will be a slap
across the face.

00:57:10.910 --> 00:57:12.740 align:middle line:84%
I don't know how
it's going to come.

00:57:12.740 --> 00:57:14.780 align:middle line:84%
The planet, we've
poisoned the water,

00:57:14.780 --> 00:57:17.090 align:middle line:90%
so there may be water issues.

00:57:17.090 --> 00:57:19.340 align:middle line:84%
We've put toxic
stuff in the air,

00:57:19.340 --> 00:57:22.370 align:middle line:90%
so there may be wind issues.

00:57:22.370 --> 00:57:24.590 align:middle line:10%
There's plenty of
reasons, and plenty

00:57:24.590 --> 00:57:26.892 align:middle line:10%
of reasons for these
elements, if you want to go in

00:57:26.892 --> 00:57:28.100 align:middle line:10%
at the very, very base level.

00:57:28.100 --> 00:57:30.370 align:middle line:10%
You know, fire,
water, earth, air.

00:57:30.370 --> 00:57:34.010 align:middle line:10%
To come back at us for
how we've treated them.

00:57:34.010 --> 00:57:37.630 align:middle line:84%
And so, whatever
is coming is big.

00:57:37.630 --> 00:57:38.769 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: I would think so.

00:57:38.769 --> 00:57:41.060 align:middle line:84%
And I think in the end, it
comes back to each one of us

00:57:41.060 --> 00:57:42.890 align:middle line:84%
to ask those questions
of ourselves, right?

00:57:42.890 --> 00:57:43.904 align:middle line:90%
>>STEVENS: Absolutely.

00:57:43.904 --> 00:57:45.570 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Any final--
